{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T17:57:14.117Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Thinking Blocks"},{"type":"text","text":" are the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks that appear in Claude's API response when extended thinking is enabled—they contain Claude's complete internal reasoning process shown transparently before delivering the final answer."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What They Are"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When extended thinking is turned on, Claude creates "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks where it outputs its internal reasoning. Claude incorporates insights from this reasoning before crafting a final response in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Structure of a Thinking Block"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"type\": \"thinking\",\n  \"thinking\": \"Let me analyze this step by step...\\nFirst, I need to understand the problem...\\nNow I'll break it down...\",\n  \"signature\": \"WaUjzkypQ2mUEVM36O2TxuC06KN8xyfbJwyem2dw3URve/op91XWHOEBLLqIOMfFG/UvLEczmEsUjavL....\"\n}"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key components:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n| Field | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"type"},{"type":"text","text":" | Must be "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"thinking\""},{"type":"text","text":" |\n| "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" | The actual reasoning content (step-by-step thought pr